nodes.text: Telbus was a bounty hunter who was active during the Galactic Civil War. He spoke a language other than Basic.

In 5 ABY, Telbus and his red-skinned acolyte were present on the planet Stenos where they tried to collect a bounty on Slider, a mercenary working for Domina Tagge. However, before they could get to him, the two bounty hunters were beaten up by Chewbacca in a bar brawl.
